<title></title>
<style type="text/css">
.main, .box{
	position: relative;
}
.main:after { 
	left: 0px;
	position: absolute; 
	background: #fff; 
	content:"支持E:after";
	width: 100%;
	}
.box::after { 
	left: 0px;
	position: absolute; 
	background: #fff; 
	content:"支持E::after";
	width: 100%;
	}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="main">
Sorry, 你的浏览器不支持E:after和E::after
</div>
<div class="box">
Sorry, 你的浏览器不支持E:after和E::after
</div>
</body>
